    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've updated the flow, it is the following:\r\n\r\n1. check if you are on branch develop\r\n2. git checkout master\r\n3. pull and merge develop into master\r\n4. build, tag, commit on master and publish to npm\r\n5. merge back master into develop and push develop\r\n6. checkout develop",
